{
  "stem": "22174.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There she-- there she wrote this feeling that she wouldn't see us anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She wouldn't see us anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll read you the card afterwards, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yeah, it was the fate of my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I always fear that I always, the rest of my life, left with a guilt feeling that I left my mother alone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'd rather have shared her fate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that's why [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'd-- ?] I'd rather have stayed with my mother until the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That much I didn't know either, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that would have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Were you able to maintain any other communication with any other family back in Germany when you were in service?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All our family left, was the extended family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was not very close, except for those two cousins in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had to be careful, you know, to-- to lay low.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and-- see-- see, one was a nurse, and she continued working as a nurse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and the other one, she was working in industry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was-- she got-- the telephone in Germany is run by the government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's not a private enterprise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not a private institution.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she worked for the telephone in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she was-- she was instrumental in-- in-- in starting the self-dialing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before that, you had to call the operator and ask for a number.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they started self-dialing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was-- she was very active in this, in-- in the beginning of this new system.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and then she worked for-- for a big industrial conglomerate-- Siemens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Siemens in [INAUDIBLE], very famous.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
